channel.title: Looking for A 718 Developer In-Game/Forums
channel.description: hello, i am currently working on a 718/742 Rsps and i am need of a In-game and forums Developer/Coder. you must be fairly familiar with java coding and 718/742 style of coding. i currently have been coding this project for over 2 months and i am at the point where i need some extra help because im getting close to finally releasing the server.I only need 2 in game developers and 1 forum developer. and yes There will be a percent of splits with donations ect once the server gets going but i will not be paying you directly before the server is up, as i only have enough money to pay for vps and forums. thanks for your time. if you would like to contact me my skype is :purecoolbow1
